title: 9 Reasons I'll Never Be A Disney Princess

Disney ID: 10260752 2. Don’t sneak up behind me while I’m grooving to music and start man-singing to me. View this image › 
Disney ID: 10259814 View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260756 3. If you wake me up while I’m sleeping, I will NOT be happy. Facebook: video.php ID: 10259790 4. I can’t ignore it when people gossip about me behind my back. Disney ID: 10259847 5. I’m not going to hop on some dude’s janky ride unless he has a license, seatbelt, and boatloads of dramamine. View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260095 6. I do not put up with this shit View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260004 7. I will not get fin-to-leg plastic surgery to please a man I’ve never had a conversation with. View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260067 8. If I’ve got seven roommates I better not be the only one cleaning. View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260237 9. If I somehow got some expensive shoes, I would never give one up. You can’t wear one shoe. View this image › 
Disney ID: 10260496 Sorry, but if the movie has a boring female lead, I’m going to fall asleep midway through. Wait, that’s exactly what Aurora did in Sleeping Beauty ? Shit, maybe I could be a Disney princess after all ;) View this image ›
